{"title":"人民普遍要求停止核试验","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":3,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民普遍要求停止核试验"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据“纽约先驱论坛报”报道，最近“世界民意测验所”在十三个国家进行了一次调查，被调查的人中有三分之二到二分之一的人同意接受苏联提出的停止核试验两年的建议。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各国同意接受苏联建议的人数比例如下："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"法国76％。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奥地利70％。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西德70％。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本67％。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑞典66％。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挪威63％。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比利时62％。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荷兰61％。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英国59％。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丹麦54％。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澳大利亚50％。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意大利48％。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴西45％。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}